nteractionMode.Auto,\n        autonomyLevel: this.store.getAutonomyLevel() ?? AutonomyLevel.Off,\n      },\n    });\n\n    this.store.setInteractionMode(next.interactionMode);\n    this.store.setAutonomyLevel(next.autonomyLevel);\n    this.store.setAutonomyMode(\n      hasDecoupledAutonomyFields\n        ? deriveAutonomyMode(next.interactionMode, next.autonomyLevel)\n        : settings.autonomyMode!\n    );\n  }\n}\n```\n\nThen replace the 3 inline copies with one-liners: `manager.applyInteractionSettings(settings)`.\n\n**Estimated: -40 net lines, 3 files.**\n\n### 2b. Add `currentInteractionMode` prop to `ModelSwitcher`\n\nOne-line logic change in `ModelSwitcher.tsx`:\n\n```ts\n// Before\nconst displayModel = currentAutonomyMode === AutonomyMode.Spec && specModeModel\n  ? specModeModel : currentModel;\n\n// After\nconst isSpecMode = currentInteractionMode !== undefined\n  ? currentInteractionMode === DroidInteractionMode.Spec\n  : currentAutonomyMode === AutonomyMode.Spec;\nconst displayModel = isSpecMode && specModeModel ? specModeModel : currentModel;\n```\n\nAdd `currentInteractionMode?: DroidInteractionMode` to `ModelSwitcherProps` and `ChatComposerModelSelectorProps`. Pass from `DroidSessionChat` via `modelSelectorProps`.\n\n**Estimated: +10 lines across 4 files.**\n\n### 2c. Add `@deprecated` JSDoc to `AutonomyModeSwitcher`\n\n2-line comment addition. No logic change. This component is V1.0-only and will die when that path is removed.\n\n---\n\n## 3. PR Strategy: Keep as One PR\n\n**Rationale:** The schema changes require all consumers (CLI, daemon, frontend) to handle the new optional fields consistently. Splitting across PRs creates a window of inconsistency. The permission fix (commit 3) is logically independent but small enough that separating it adds review overhead without real benefit.\n\n**Commit structure (reorder for reviewability):**\n1. `fix(cli): centralize permission outcome handling` -- self-contained behavioral fix, easiest to review\n2. `refa